                    <h2 class="case-title">BPN Paribas</h2>
                    <p class="case-text">Affinity offers the most comprehensive optimisation services and works with the largest 2G/3G/4G mobile telecommunication operators and manufacturers worldwide.</p>
                    <p class="case-text">Generally speaking, our services include:
                        — Process analysis to increase the level of accuracy of existing data;
                        — Measuring the network coverage levels (Drivetests);

                        — Optimisation in line with the defined KPIs;
                        Validation of parametrization;
                        Certification of quality of service (QoS).
                    </p>
                    <p class="case-text">We provide preventive and corrective services to ensure the top quality of telecommunication services. Our knowledge and experience enable us to achieve our main objective: improve the network performance of our partners, directly impacting on the satisfaction of their end-clients.
